          <text><![CDATA[<p><b><b>Hospital Opioid Solutions Toolkit Act of 2018 or the HOST Act of 2018</b></b></p> <p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to publish guidance for hospitals on pain management and opioid-use disorder prevention strategies for Medicare beneficiaries, including best practices for opioid-use disorder screening, education, and monitoring. </p>]]></text>
